TextEng: Me is going, now.
I was just leaving.
You get out of way! Me goes where me wants!!
Text: 너 비켜! 나 가고 싶은 데 가!!

TextEng: Get out of my way! I'll go where I please!
Text: 비키세요! 가고 싶은 데 갈 거니까!

TextEng: Maybe me gonna do that! You gives gold or you die!
Text: 그래 그럴까! 금화 내놔 안 그러면 죽어!

TextEng: Perhaps I will! Give me all your gold or die!
Text: 그래 그럴까! 금화 다 내놔요 안 그러면 죽어!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me city guard. Mean no harm.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 도시 경비병. 해치려는 거 아냐.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I'm with the city guard, I don't mean any harm.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 도시 경비대 소속이에요, 해칠 생각 없어요.

TextEng: Goodbye.
Me want ask questions.
Could I ask you some questions?
Me collects gold to protect nobles. See, nobles die in they own homes all the time.
Text: 나 귀족 보호하려고 금화 모아. 있잖아, 귀족들 집에서 맨날 죽어.

TextEng: I'm collecting gold to protect nobles. Many are killed in their own homes everyday.
Text: 귀족 보호를 위해 금화를 모으고 있어요. 매일 자기 집에서 죽는 사람이 많거든요.

TextEng: Me just leave nows. Sorry to bothers.
Text: 나 이제 가. 귀찮게 해서 미안.

TextEng: I'll just leave. Sorry to bother you.
Maybe me just go back to other questions.
Perhaps I should just go back to my other questions.
Hypotemi... hippo...uh, yes! Unless you donate, you could die! AT ANY SECOND!
Text: 가상으... 가정...어, 맞아! 기부 안 하면 죽을 수 있어! 당장이라도!

TextEng: Hypothetically? Yes. Unless you "donate," you could die. Maybe even RIGHT NOW! Or NOW!
Text: 가정적으로요? 네. "기부"하지 않으면 죽을 수도 있어요. 바로 지금이라도! 아니면 지금!

TextEng: Me need directions.
Can I ask you some directions?
No, me have other question.
Actually, I'd rather ask you about something else.
Me need place to buy stuff. Is there one here somewheres?
Text: 나 물건 살 데 필요해. 이 근처에 있어?

TextEng: Is there a place to buy equipment nearby?
Me look for temple.
Where is the nearest temple?
Me look for place to sleep.
Where is the nearest inn?
You know 'bout any weird stuff here in Blacklake place?
Do you know of anything interesting going on in Blacklake?
Places in Blacklake I should go to?
Any places in Blacklake you think I should visit?
Me want work.
I'd be interested in work, if you know of anything.
Text: 일거리가 있다면 관심 있는데요, 혹시 아시는 거 있어요?

TextEng: Any weird stuff at all?
Anything peculiar that you can think of?
Ooooo, come on handsome guy, talks about it.
Are you sure you couldn't say, handsome?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Tell me. Will hurt nobody.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Come now, telling me won't do any harm.
Me look into plague. Maybe you help?
Text: 나 역병 조사해. 도와줄 수 있어?

TextEng: I'm investigating the plague. Perhaps you can help me?
Text: 역병을 조사하고 있어요. 도와주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: Me have other question.
I want to ask you something else.
You hear plague rumors, maybe?
Have you heard any rumors concerning the plague?
Text: 역병에 관한 소문 들으신 거 있어요?

TextEng: You know 'bout strange creatures around?
Are you aware of any strange creatures in the area?
Nothing weird about zoo?
So there's been nothing odd about the zoo, then?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Is it possible that some creatures might have gained access to the zoo, somehow?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 혹시 어떤 생명체가 동물원에 침입했을 가능성은 없나요?
